info.title: eQRito
info.description: Create beautiful customized, colored, QR Code in svg,  pdf, png, jpeg, webp format.
info.x-long-description:
Many cells, eye frames and balls type available.
Colored QR with gradients. One simple api endpoint !
Multiple output format : png, pdf, svg, jpeg, webp

post.operationId: Create beautiful QR code in one request
post.description: This endpoints creates your QRcode as an image in many format and with many options
